These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, aquamarine, amber, lilac
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, comedy, adventure, spy
1. the person who likes amber is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
2. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
3. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person watching adventure movies##8
4. the person watching comedy movies is not the person who likes amber##6
5. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
6. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Color   | lilac  | emerald | amber | aquamarine  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | adventure   | spy  | comedy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, sudoku, video-games, cooking
4 different games are played: chess, scrabble, whist, poker
1. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
2. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
3. the person who's hobby is camping is the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person playing chess##7
6. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
7. the person playing chess is not to the left of the person playing chess##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | sudoku          | cooking | camping     |
| Game    | whist      | poker | chess | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, polish, french, colombian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, juice, fanta
1. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the french##8
2. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
3. the polish is on the right of the british##1
4. the polish is in an even position##4
5. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the british is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
7. the colombian is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality           | british | polish | french     | colombian |
| Beverage   | milk    | fanta   | coffee | juice    |

