.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, camping, writing, filmmaking
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris, daisy, lily
1. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growslily##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is not to the left of the person who growsiris##8
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who growsmarigold##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Hobby   | writing   | camping         | filmmaking   | video-games    |
| Flower         | iris | lily | daisy | marigold |

