.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, nurse, freelancer, social-worker
City: berlin, miami, prague, marseilles
1. the social-worker is somewhere between the manager and the nurse##7
2. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
3. the social-worker is somewhere between the freelancer and the manager##7
4. the freelancer is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8
5. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere between the nurse and the person traveling to miami##7
6. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the right of the social-worker##5
7. the person traveling to miami is not to the left of the manager##8
8. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the social-worker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Job   | nurse   | freelancer | social-worker | manager    |
| City         | berlin | marseilles   | prague   | miami |

