.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, sunflower, begonia
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, havana, old-henry, fonseca
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
5. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the person who growsrose##5
6. the person who growsbegonia is not to the left of the havana-smoker##8
7. the person who growsbegonia is the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Flower          | begonia | daffodil | rose  | sunflower |
| Cigar   | havana   | fonseca         | old-henry | alhambra |

