.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, azalea, amaryllis, marigold
4 different pets are kept: fish, dog, hamster, bird
1. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person who growsazalea##8
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the person who growsmarigold and the owner of the hamster##7
3. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
4. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the owner of the fish##8
5. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the person who growsazalea##8
6. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
7. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
8. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Flower   | azalea      | amaryllis | rose | marigold   |
| Pet      | fish | hamster | bird  | dog |

