.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, quad-bike, snowmobile
4 different games are played: billiard, poker, go, monopoly
1. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8
2. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing go is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person driving the bike##7
5. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
6. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person driving the quad-bike##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Transport     | bike | quad-bike | snowmobile | airplane     |
| Game   | billiard   | go        | monopoly          | poker |

