.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, action, comedy, spy
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, cain, ritmeester, swisher
1. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching spy movies and the chaman-smoker##2
2. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
4. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the chaman-smoker##5
5. the cain-smoker is the cain-smoker##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is not the ritmeester-smoker##6
7. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the person watching comedy movies##8
8. the chaman-smoker is not to the left of the cain-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy   | epic | comedy | action |
| Cigar     | swisher | cain       | chaman  | ritmeester    |

