2. the gothic-revival house is not the person who's hobby is reading##6
3. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
6. the palace house is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | traveling | video-games      | rock-climbing   | reading  |
| House   | cottage    | palace | gothic-revival | wooden |

