.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-11::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, chess, whist, snooker
There 4 different types of food: potato, apricot, pomegranate, carrot
1. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
2. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
3. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person eating carrot##5
4. the person eating carrot is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8
5. the person eating apricot is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
6. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Game   | monopoly     | snooker | whist | chess |
| Food     | pomegranate | carrot  | apricot    | potato   |

