.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, ambient, metal, house
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, soy-milk, juice
1. the fan of metal is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
2. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the fan of house##5
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of metal is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking soy-milk##2
6. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
7. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre    | ambient        | house | metal      | salsa    |
| Beverage   | mirinda | soy-milk   | iced-tea | juice |

