2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the right of the person traveling to paris##8
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is camping and the person traveling to colone##7
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| City   | edinburgh | colone         | london    | paris       |
| Hobby      | reading | magic-tricks | card-games | camping |

