 3. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 9. the person drinking mirinda is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
10. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the left of the person drinking juice##8

