2. the person watching zombie movies is not to the right of the person who likes grey##8
3. the person who likes mauve is somewhere between the person who likes grey and the person who likes green##7
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
6. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
7. the person who likes mauve is not to the left of the person watching musical movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Color         | turquise  | green | mauve  | grey  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | martial-arts   | musical | zombie |

