.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bongani, cain, ritmeester
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, chess, woodworking, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is chess is not the game-smoker##6
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
4. the cain-smoker is the person who's hobby is reading##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is reading##7
6. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the cain-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar         | bongani    | ritmeester | game | cain |
| Hobby   | chess | skydiving      | woodworking     | reading     |

 